Text:
Don't bother with this shit. I hate fucking retarded Dj's like this who do absolutely nothing but add their fucking name to a song.

I hate to break it to you, but adding your name in a song you didn't even bother remixing at all doesn't make you a DJ it makes you a sad wannabe fool.

Fucking listening to this and all of a sudden some voice goes "DJ Finesse" it's fucking annoying, sad, and if you do have a job DJing somewhere it must be the worst place ever to hire a DJ like this.
